oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall and an unidentified soldier smoking in an office
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of an unidentified male solider smoking a cigarette while Kinsall is smoking a pipe in an office. The shoulder sleeve insignia of the United States Army Air Forces can be seen on their uniforms.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Kinsall, J.Y.
